      <title>日本首次向俄罗斯军用飞机发射照明弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/in-a-first-japan-fires-flares-against-russian-military-aircraft</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本战斗机向一架俄罗斯军用飞机发射警告信号弹，东京方面称，该飞机多次进入日本领空，这是针对外国飞机采取的前所未有的行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/in-a-first-japan-fires-flares-against-russian-military-aircraft</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 01:30:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普称将在联合国会议前以“不同方式”处理乌克兰问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/trump-says-he-d-handle-ukraine-differently-ahead-of-un-meeting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党总统候选人唐纳德·特朗普表示，他将“以不同的方式”对待乌克兰政策，并对乌克兰总统弗拉基米尔·泽连斯基的安全援助请求感到惊讶。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/trump-says-he-d-handle-ukraine-differently-ahead-of-un-meeting</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 01:03:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡将对前部长易华兰贪污案展开里程碑式审判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/singapore-to-start-landmark-graft-trial-of-ex-minister-iswaran</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新加坡前交通部长腐败案备受期待的审判将于周二开始，该城市国家正在应对近四十年来最大的政治丑闻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/singapore-to-start-landmark-graft-trial-of-ex-minister-iswaran</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>盟友卢汉·格里沙姆称哈里斯应该继续担任拜登内阁职务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/harris-should-keep-biden-s-cabinet-ally-lujan-grisham-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新墨西哥州州长米歇尔·卢汉·格里沙姆表示，如果民主党候选人卡玛拉·哈里斯在 11 月击败唐纳德·特朗普，她应该保留乔·拜登内阁的大部分成员。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/harris-should-keep-biden-s-cabinet-ally-lujan-grisham-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 23:23:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡总理警告中美竞争“乌云密布”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/singapore-pm-wong-warns-of-dark-clouds-as-us-china-compete</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新加坡总理黄循财警告称，随着越来越多的全球经济活动从安全角度进行审视，地平线上将出现“乌云”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/singapore-pm-wong-warns-of-dark-clouds-as-us-china-compete</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 22:39:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
